## Description

The **Webhook Triggers** component provides a standard webhook trigger that allows integrations to be executed via an HTTP POST request.

## Triggers

<div id="webhook" />

### Webhook

Executes an integration via an HTTP Post request to a URL | <small><b>key: webhook</b></small>
